1131
00:44:19,011 --> 00:44:21,641
I was young then.

1132
00:44:22,341 --> 00:44:23,610
- I can't do that now.
- You're still young.

1133
00:44:23,611 --> 00:44:24,851
I can't do that now.

1134
00:44:26,511 --> 00:44:30,381
