- Give it to me.

1187
00:46:44,221 --> 00:46:45,921
I have really low blood pressure.

1188
00:46:46,091 --> 00:46:47,660
Really? Measure it here.

1189
00:46:47,661 --> 00:46:50,321
Mine is 50 over 70.

1190
00:46:51,261 --> 00:46:52,930
