- Okay.

1210
00:47:40,741 --> 00:47:41,911
Let's go.

1211
00:47:42,141 --> 00:47:46,711
(Feeling sad)

1212
00:47:47,681 --> 00:47:51,451
(Don't be sick, My Star!)

1213
00:47:53,491 --> 00:47:55,360
